source.name: IMVU Credit Resellers List
source.description: A list of IMVU Credit resellers. IMVU is a popular 3D chatting room site with its own virtual economy and currency. This list is here to provide those looking to purchase or sell IMVU Credits a way to compare major resellers so that they can get the best deal when buying or selling credits.
